1
00:00:01,233 --> 00:00:03,433
Sorry that I failed to mention your exams.

2
00:00:03,873 --> 00:00:05,900
I was busy dealing with some of Shido's
cronies.

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:10,340
Well, you are students, so it's only
fitting you're doing a study group.

4
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:13,660
You're gonna bring us some snacks now and
then, right?

5
00:00:15,833 --> 00:00:17,220
You don't even have exams.

6
00:00:21,580 --> 00:00:22,860
Pardon the intrusion.

7
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:25,860
Glad to see you all.

8
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:27,380
Don't mind me.

9
00:00:27,420 --> 00:00:28,500
Make yourselves at home.

10
00:00:29,540 --> 00:00:30,680
You're too kind.

11
00:00:30,980 --> 00:00:32,500
We'll take you up on that offer.

12
00:00:33,620 --> 00:00:35,120
Why did you bring me here?

13
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,060
My school's exams are already over.

14
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,780
Come on, don't be so cold.

15
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,620
You're saying it's fine if I fail?

16
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:43,720
Nothing wrong with that.

17
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:47,620
Won't the results be the same whether you
study or not?

18
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:50,000
Now, now, you guys.

19
00:00:50,360 --> 00:00:52,200
Just think of it as helping me out.

20
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:54,940
I don't know about this.

21
00:00:57,089 --> 00:01:00,580
I'm just going to focus on sections that
may likely be on the test.

22
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,360
You're way too short on time.

23
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,840
Making a gamble, huh?

24
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,840
If she's wrong, we die.

25
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:10,840
Aw, I don't wanna die.

26
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:14,740
Um, is it really that bad?

27
00:01:15,780 --> 00:01:17,440
This is every day for them.

28
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:20,693
This affects you, too.

